            <title>[CAMEL-11889] Kie assumes that the TCCL can load its services</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-11889</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The recent update of optaplanner comes with kit-7.3.0.final, which relies on the TCCL&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/kiegroup/droolsjbpm-knowledge/blob/7.3.0.Final/kie-api/src/main/java/org/kie/api/internal/utils/ServiceDiscoveryImpl.java#L163&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/kiegroup/droolsjbpm-knowledge/blob/7.3.0.Final/kie-api/src/main/java/org/kie/api/internal/utils/ServiceDiscoveryImpl.java#L163&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Perhaps, this can be fixed at the camel-optaplanner  component level. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
